## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- We will test the API endpoints locally using PowerShell `Invoke-RestMethod` to ensure the Vanilla Node.js server connects to MySQL correctly and executes queries.

### Manual Verification
- Start the server (`node server.js`).
- Open [index.html](file:///c:/Users/GOZA/OneDrive/Codes/Antigavity/JS-MVC/index.html) in the browser (or run via a simple local server if CORS requires it).
- Add, edit, and delete contacts in the UI and verify that the changes persist to the MySQL database by refreshing the page and checking the data.
